BFHL REST API

This project implements the BFHL Qualifier REST API as required for the Chitkara University 2026 evaluation.

The application exposes two public endpoints:

GET /health

POST /bfhl

The API is built using Node.js and Express and includes structured validation, centralized error handling, and external AI integration using Google Gemini.

Live Deployment

